ow glasswort | ''[[Salicornia fragilis]]'' | |- | Long-spiked glasswort | ''[[Salicornia dolichostachya]]'' | |- | Shrubby sea-blite | ''[[Suaeda vera]]'' | |- | Annual sea-blite | ''[[Suaeda maritima]]'' | |- | Prickly saltwort | ''[[Salsola kali]]'' | |}
