==Notes== # Fringed sandwort (''Arenaria ciliata'') is found only in Ireland. # Recurved sandwort (''Minuartia recurva'') is found only in Ireland. # Corn spurrey (''Spergula arvensis'') is an [[archaeophyte]] in Britain and Ireland; a native population exists on the [[Channel Islands]]
