==Delaware== [[Image:Sandy Oct 29 2012 1815Z (cropped).jpg|thumb|right|250px|Hurricane Sandy]] A large swath of heavy rainfall spread associated with a predecessor rainfall event fell before [[1933 Chesapeake–Potomac hurricane]] arrived in Delaware. Over four days, a total of {{convert|13.24|in}} of rain fell in Bridgeville, the most known associated with a tropical cyclone anywhere in Delaware.<ref name="Rain pre 50s"/>
