==Kansas== Heavy rainfall from [[Tropical Storm Frances (1998)|Tropical Storm Frances]] fell from the western [[Gulf Coast]] northward into the [[Great Plains]]. Spreading across portions of [[Kansas]], precipitation included with localized amounts above {{convert|12|in|mm}}.<ref name="Mid West"/> [[File:Frances 1998-09-10 1845Z.png|thumb|right|250 px|Tropical Storm Frances (1998)]]
