==Massachusetts== The wettest known tropical cyclone to impact [[New England]] is also the wettest known for the state of [[Massachusetts]].<ref name="WPCMAX"/> The flood from [[Hurricane Diane]] led to a significant death toll (nearly 200) from Pennsylvania eastward through southern New England.<ref name=Diane/> [[Image:Carrie 1972.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|Tropical Storm Carrie (1972)]]
