==Michigan== In 1961, Hurricane Carla generated more precipitation in [[Michigan]] than any other tropical cyclone has ever generated in the state. Carla is also the wettest tropical cyclone to have hit [[Iowa]], [[Nebraska]], and [[Wisconsin]].<ref name="Mid West"/> [[File:Chantal 1989-08-01 1501Z.png|thumb|right|250 px|Hurricane Chantal (1989)]]
