==Minnesota== Few tropical cyclone remnants originating from the eastern Pacific or Atlantic Basins make it as far north as [[Minnesota]]. Most recently, 2004's [[Hurricane Javier (2004)|Hurricane Javier]] dropped heavy rainfall exceeding {{convert|2|in|mm}} in localized spots.<ref name="Mid West"/> [[File:Hurricane javier 2004.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|Hurricane Javier (2004)]]
