==Montana== It is rare for tropical cyclone remnants originating from the eastern Pacific or Atlantic Basins to make it as far north as [[Montana]]. The remains of [[Hurricane Kathleen (1976)|Kathleen]] dropped locally heavy rainfall approaching {{convert|2|in|mm}} in localized spots.<ref name="Western"/> [[Image:KathleenSeptember919760415UTC.gif|thumb|right|250 px|Hurricane Kathleen (1976)]]
