==Nebraska== The wettest known event in [[Nebraska]] to be associated with a tropical cyclone or its remains was Hurricane Carla. Carla resulted in the heaviest known rainfall in several other states as well.<ref name="Mid West"/> [[Image:Hurricane Lester 22 aug 1992 2246Z.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|Hurricane Lester (1992)]]
