==Nevada== Every few years, Nevada is impacted by eastern Pacific tropical cyclones, or their remnants. The wettest known event for the state was during [[1977 Pacific hurricane season#Hurricane Doreen|Hurricane Doreen]], when over {{convert|4|in|mm}} fell in isolated spots.<ref name="Western"/> [[File:Norman 1978-09-02 1800Z.png|thumb|right|250px|Norman (1978)]] <!--Using wpc rainfall data only-->
