ern"/> |- | 10 || {{convert|2.17|in|mm|disp=table|order=flip|sigfig=4}} || [[Hurricane Lester (1992)|Lester 1992]] || Lindrith 1 WSW ||<ref name="Western"/> |} {{clear}}
==New York== Tropical cyclones moving up the East Coast bring rainfall to [[New York (state)|New York]] frequently. During [[Hurricane Connie]], over {{convert|13|in|mm}} fell in isolated spots, which was the most rainfall recorded with a tropical cyclone or its remains across the state.<ref name="Irene2011PA37"/><ref name="Mid Atl"/> [[Image:Hurricane irene 082811 0832 edt.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|Hurricane Irene]]
