==South Dakota== It is rare for tropical cyclone remnants originating from the eastern Pacific or Atlantic Basins to move as far inland as [[South Dakota]]. The remains of [[Hurricane Javier (2004)|Javier in 2004]] dropped locally heavy rainfall exceeding {{convert|2|in|mm}} in localized spots.<ref name="Mid West"/> [[Image:Hurricane Lester 22 aug 1992 2246Z.jpg|thumb|right|250px|Hurricane Lester (1992)]]
