==Wyoming== Few tropical cyclone remnants originating from the eastern Pacific make it as far north as [[Wyoming]]. Most recently, [[Hurricane Javier (2004)|Hurricane Javier]] dropped locally heavy rainfall of up to {{convert|2|in|mm}} in the higher terrain of western Wyoming.<ref name="Western"/> [[Image:Hurricane javier 2004.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|Javier (2004)]]
