{{Infobox power station |name = Salem Harbor Power Station |image = Salem Harbor Station Natural Gas Plant.jpg |image_caption = Current facility built by Footprint Power |location_map = USA Massachusetts |country = United States |location = [[Salem, Massachusetts]] | coordinates = {{coord|42|31|34.73|N|70|52|35.42|W|region:US-MA_type:landmark|display=inline,title}} |owner = |status = }}
'''Salem Harbor Power Station''' is a natural gas-fired power plant located in [[Salem, Massachusetts]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Salem Harbor Footprint|url=http://www.footprintsalemharbor.com/|website=Footprint Power|accessdate=2 June 2016}}</ref> It replaced an outdated coal-fired plant on the same site and went online in May 2018.<ref>{{cite web|title=Salem power plant online |url=http://www.salemnews.com/news/local_news/salem-power-plant-online/article_e610c4dc-884b-5f8d-ab91-3cb497839e8c.html|website=Salem News|accessdate=12 June 2018}}</ref>
The facility sits on [[land reclamation|land reclaimed]] during the 1800s, and was previously the site of a wharf and [[coal]] depository. Construction on the original plant began in the 1950s, and was expanded numerous times. [[File:Salem Harbor Station.jpg|thumb|left|Original coal-fired plant in 2012]] It is smaller than the original plant, allowing 40-acres of waterfront land to be used for future development. The 60-year-old coal plant, which was purchased by Footprint Power in 2012, was brought offline on May 31, 2014. Demolition work was completed in 2016, while the new plant was being built around it.<ref name=Helms>{{cite news|last=Helms|first=Chris|title=Salem Harbor Power Station CEO Touts Design of New Facility|url=http://marblehead.patch.com/articles/salem-harbor-power-station-ceo-touts-design-of-new-facility-b6d04fb7|accessdate=5 May 2013|newspaper=Marblehead Patch|date=7 February 2013|location=[[Salem, Massachusetts]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130630030345/http://marblehead.patch.com/articles/salem-harbor-power-station-ceo-touts-design-of-new-facility-b6d04fb7|archivedate=30 June 2013|df=}}</ref>
